ZH: 能人是指擅長做事情的人。
EN: A talented person is someone who excels at tasks.
ZH: 他是一位能人，贏得了比賽的冠軍。
EN: He is a talented person who won the championship.
ZH: 她是我認識的一位能人，每次都能處理問題。
EN: She is a talented person I know who can handle problems every time.
ZH: 這位能人在音樂上有非凡的才華。
EN: This talented person has extraordinary talent in music.
ZH: 我們需要更多的能人來參加這個項目。
EN: We need more talented individuals to participate in this project.
ZH: 這個團隊裡有好幾位能人在技術上非常厲害。
EN: There are several talented individuals in this team who are very skilled in technology.
ZH: 公司裡的能人都有機會獲得晉升。
EN: Talented individuals in the company have the opportunity for promotion.
ZH: 這些能人的意見對我們的決策非常重要。
EN: The opinions of these talented individuals are very important for our decision-making.
ZH: 當你遇到問題時，找一位能人來幫助你是最好的選擇。
EN: When you encounter problems, it is best to seek help from a talented person.
ZH: 這位能人已經獲得了多個獎項以表彰他的才華。
EN: This talented individual has won multiple awards to recognize his talent.
ZH: 請問你是一位能人嗎？
EN: Excuse me, are you a talented person?
ZH: 他被稱為這個行業的能人，深受人們的尊重。
EN: He is known as a talented person in this industry and is deeply respected by people.
ZH: 在這個競爭激烈的市場中，只有能人才能立足。
EN: In this competitive market, only talented individuals can succeed.
ZH: 這位能人在創造新想法方面非常有天賦。
EN: This talented individual is very gifted in generating new ideas.
ZH: 請問這個專案需要多少位能人參與？
EN: How many talented individuals are needed to participate in this project?
ZH: 能人定能遇到更多機會讓他們發揮才華。
EN: Talented individuals will surely encounter more opportunities to showcase their talents.
ZH: 這群能人是我們的驕傲。
EN: This group of talented individuals is our pride.
ZH: 這次比賽的勝出者將被譽為本年度的最佳能人。
EN: The winner of this competition will be hailed as the best talented individual of the year.
